div class=\"tcs-review-block\">\n          <span class=\"tcs-label-pill\">Snapshot \u2022 Risk Overview</span>\n          <h2>Is Wageon Casino Safe to Play?</h2>\n          <p>\n            Based on our internal scoring data, Wageon Casino presents\n            <strong>critical risk indicators</strong> that significantly impact its overall rating.\n          </p>\n\n          <div style=\"display:grid; grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr; gap:20px;\">\n            <div>\n              <h3>Observed Issues</h3>\n              <ul>\n                <li>No verifiable gaming licence identified.</li>\n                <li>Platform structure mirrors an existing casino without clear differentiation.</li>\n                <li>Failure to meet accepted operational standards.</li>\n              </ul>\n            </div>\n            <div>\n              <h3>Missing Protections</h3>\n              <ul>\n                <li>No confirmed regulatory oversight.</li>\n                <li>No reliable dispute resolution mechanism.</li>\n                <li>Insufficient transparency regarding player rights.</li>\n              </ul>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n\n        <div class=\"tcs-review-block\">\n          <span class=\"tcs-label-pill\">Bonuses</span>\n          <h2>Wageon Casino Bonus Assessment</h2>\n          <p>\n            Promotional offers may be displayed on the platform; however, due to unresolved\n            concerns around legitimacy and standards, bonus participation is considered\n            high-risk.\n          </p>\n        </div>\n\n      </div>\n\n      <!-- RIGHT -->\n      <div>\n\n        <div class=\"tcs-review-block\">\n          <span class=\"tcs-label-pill\">Safety</span>\n          <h2>Licensing &amp; Regulatory Status</h2>\n          <p>\n            No valid gaming licence was identified during our review.\n            This places Wageon Casino outside accepted regulatory frameworks\n            used by trusted online casinos.\n